    "name": "Kyoukai",
    "steam_appid": 3164190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras/713f73cffbe933773a1938811752d79c.avif?t=1765311154\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras_big/713f73cffbe933773a1938811752d79c.avif?t=1765311154 width=800 height=411 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Kyoukai ECG Online, the online client for the IsoRPG-inspired TCG! Kyoukai is designed to be a printed Card Game, has no mana resource, and no AI of any kind. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras/b96f7be1145177d6f369c9f60cfe56d7.avif?t=1765311154\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras_big/b96f7be1145177d6f369c9f60cfe56d7.avif?t=1765311154 width=800 height=373 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an Entrant in a fighting tournament, run by the mysterious Carnation Society. Called through the Gate into a mysterious new world, you build a deck of 40 Cards (or Gates), and up to 15 Spirits, and battle other Entrants in various online lobbies! You can also learn more about the lore and world of Kyoukai through single player visual novels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras/c03048e054cd3b93f0d271aafc6d83eb.avif?t=1765311154\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras_big/c03048e054cd3b93f0d271aafc6d83eb.avif?t=1765311154 width=800 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique diagonal Gates are played on a diamond 5x5 grid, and familiar mechanics lie at the heart of fast-paced card battles. Each turn, each of your Units has a standard action - they can first move, then either Attack or use their Skill. You can also build your field presence by Opening Gates from your hand - but you can only Open them next to your Ready Gates already on the field. Use your on-field Units, and Normal and Fast Gates from your hand, to approach your opponent's Entrant and deal 20 damage to them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras/e8e1bc03a6c1eb48cc7d23188a335cc3.avif?t=1765311154\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras_big/e8e1bc03a6c1eb48cc7d23188a335cc3.avif?t=1765311154 width=800 height=373 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 5 Entrants, each with their own unique card pool and deck types! Find your own unique take on your favorite Entrant, or get started with one of each Entrant's multiple pre-build starter decks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras/256370e324a942133a8a3843feb12a65.avif?t=1765311154\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164190/extras_big/256370e324a942133a8a3843feb12a65.avif?t=1765311154 width=800 height=373 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All playable Gates will be available as soon as you download Kyoukai! There will be no unlocks or in-game currency. <i>  </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
